
== About this readme ==

This readme is mostly meant for developers. If you are looking for information
on how to install leihs on your own server, please see the administration
guide in this directory.


== Developing leihs ==

Please see our project page (especially the wiki) for information about leihs 
that might be interesting for developers.

You can find the project page at:

http://code.zhdk.ch/projects/leihs


The pages about terminology and models might be the best starting place for
new developers:

http://code.zhdk.ch/projects/leihs/wiki/Terminology
http://code.zhdk.ch/projects/leihs/wiki/Models


For installation and system administration guides, please see the help page:

http://code.zhdk.ch/projects/leihs/wiki/Help
